    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "It is important to note that the kernel can be in all of these contexts at once.  It is quite reasonable to have a fully capable notebook, with a qtconsole and ASCII-locale zmq terminal connected to it.  I do this fairly regularly (excluding the restricted locale in the terminal session).\n"
